Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.48,0:32:17.98,birthcertificate2,,0,310,158,,Šimomura Kazuo
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.48,0:32:17.98,birthcertificate2,,530,0,165,,Šimomura Kazuo
